hwVoRasOn.name: hwVoRasOn
hwVoRasOn.description: This object expresses whether or not the GKClient function of this gateaway is enabled .Before hwVoGwIPAddress and hwVoH323GKID being set ,this object can not be set to enable.

hwVoH323InterfaceIndex.name: hwVoH323InterfaceIndex
hwVoH323InterfaceIndex.description: The index of the interface through which the gateway is connected to the GateKeeper.

hwVoGwIPAddress.name: hwVoGwIPAddress
hwVoGwIPAddress.description: This object expresses the IP address of the interface through which the gateway is connected to the GateKeeper.

hwVoH323GWID.name: hwVoH323GWID
hwVoH323GWID.description: This object expresses the ID of this H323 gateway .

hwVoH323GWSupportMode.name: hwVoH323GWSupportMode
hwVoH323GWSupportMode.description: This object expresses the type of GateKeeper to which this H323 gateway is connected .

hwVoH323GWAreaID.name: hwVoH323GWAreaID
hwVoH323GWAreaID.description: This object expresses the technology prefixs of this gateway so that the GateKeeper can validation the type of gateway .There are thirty prefixs which can be configed in one gateway.In this object every prefix is seperated by a ';'.As a single prefix , only character from '0' to '9' and '#' can present,its length is limited to 31.

hwVoH323GKID.name: hwVoH323GKID
hwVoH323GKID.description: This object expresses the ID of the GateKeeper .

hwVoH323GKIPAddress.name: hwVoH323GKIPAddress
hwVoH323GKIPAddress.description: This object expresses the IP address of the GateKeeper .

hwVoH323GKPort.name: hwVoH323GKPort
hwVoH323GKPort.description: This object expresses the RAS communication port of GateKeeper.

hwVoH323GK2ID.name: hwVoH323GK2ID
hwVoH323GK2ID.description: This object expresses the ID of the Slave GateKeeper .

hwVoH323GK2IPAddress.name: hwVoH323GK2IPAddress
hwVoH323GK2IPAddress.description: This object expresses the IP address of the Slave GateKeeper .

hwVoH323GK2Port.name: hwVoH323GK2Port
hwVoH323GK2Port.description: This object expresses the RAS communication port of Slave GateKeeper.

hwVoH323GKSecurityPWDType.name: hwVoH323GKSecurityPWDType
hwVoH323GKSecurityPWDType.description: Specify registration level security Type cipher Hide the password when showing simple Don't hide the password when showing

hwVoH323GKSecurityPWD.name: hwVoH323GKSecurityPWD
hwVoH323GKSecurityPWD.description: register password. length 0 : clear password;disable GKSecurity Capacity. length 1-16: set password with no encrypted text. length 24: set password with encrypted text.
